{"SELFISH":[{"def":"Believing or teaching that the chief motives of human action are derived from love of self.","pos":""}],"SELFISHLY":[{"def":"In a selfish manner; with regard to private interest only or chiefly.","pos":""}],"SELFISHNESS":[{"def":"The quality or state of being selfish; exclusive regard to one's own interest or happiness; that supreme self-love or self- preference which leads a person to direct his purposes to the advancement of his own interest, power, or happiness, without regarding those of others.","pos":""}],"SELFISM":[{"def":"Concentration of one's interests on one's self; self-love; selfishness.","pos":""}],"SELFIST":[{"def":"A selfish person.","pos":""}]}